== 1...e5 ==
Black takes space in the centre. 

If White responds [[/2. d4|'''2. d4''']], a reversed [[Chess Opening Theory/1. e4/1...e6/2. d4|French defence]] position is arrived at, more usually seen in the [[Chess Opening Theory/1. d4/1...e5/2. e3|Englund gambit declined with e3]]. 

[[/2. e4|'''2. e4?!''']] appears to reach the usual position seen after 1. e4 e5, the Open game--except this time it's Black to move. 

